      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new horror anthology and I'm stuck on the setting for one of my stories. I want to do something that feels very \"urban\" and gritty, like a place where you can feel the tension just walking down the street. Can you help me brainstorm some ideas for a \"haunted\" or cursed neighborhood that feels genuinely dangerous and unsettling?",
